headline: Finance and HR Software Stocks Q4 Recap: Benchmarking Bill.com (NYSE:BILL)
summary: Quarterly earnings results are a good time to check in on a company’s progress, especially compared to its peers in the same sector. Today we are looking at Bill.com (NYSE:BILL) and the best and worst performers in the finance and hr software industry.
